  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Supporting the Young Generation Journalists, Moldovan Media&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99;s Future . Independent Journalism Center&apos;s Chisinau School of Advanced Journalism conducts courses for aspiring journalists of Moldova. The classes are mimicking a working newsroom with practical assignments for each course, teamwork and real life journalistic stories. Courses are complete with a practical work and a public presentation of the final, long-format journalistic piece. Project&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99;s goal is to train more professional journalists working for media organizations in Moldova. Overall objectives are the further professionalization of the media in Moldova and better informed public in Moldova. Keywords: independent media, democratisation.</narrative>
  </description>
